OL,3,CUniversity apologises after using
OL,4,Ccontroversial autism symbol
OL,6,FA university has apologised after
OL,7,Fusing a symbol deemed offensive to
OL,8,Fpeople with autism.
OL,10,FThe shared a post on its social media
OL,11,Fpages on Tuesday, 2 April, to
OL,12,Fhighlight World Autism Awareness Day.
OL,14,FThe post included an image of a jigsaw
OL,15,Fpuzzle piece, formerly widely used as
OL,16,Fa representation of autism awareness.
OL,18,FIn recent years the symbol has become
OL,19,Fa subject of controversy.
