OL,3,CUniversity apologises after using
OL,4,Ccontroversial autism symbol
OL,6,FSocial media users criticised the
OL,7,Funiversity following the post and it
OL,8,Fhas since been removed.
OL,10,FThe university apologised and said it
OL,11,Fhas "clear gaps in our knowledge and
OL,12,Funderstanding".
OL,14,FThe statement added: "Yesterday, we
OL,15,Fshared an autism awareness post.
OL,16,FWithin the image, we used a puzzle
OL,17,Fpiece symbol, which understandably
OL,18,Fcaused upset to some people. We are
OL,19,Fvery sorry to have caused this.
